{
  "stem": "19218.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're coming into a camp, you're coming into a camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a working camp, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't dare even ask, what's happening there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Were we going to see our parents, our sisters, our brothers?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't even answer us to that question.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the Germans were brutal from the beginning, the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I shouldn't say Germans, of course they were German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I knew, they were German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were brutal right from the start, constantly beating us-- constantly, constantly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, when we arrived into Birkenau, the following day we were all tattooed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were supposedly lining up in alphabetical order.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother went, of course, before me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was the second one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And his number was 98,909.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My tattoo on my arm reads 98,910, which means actual reality I was the 98,910th person arriving into the workforce, into the camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm quite sure there were many, many, many, many more which came in but they never made it even to the number.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they only picked the strongest ones that they thought they could still work, they could still get some-- they still could be some use to the Third Reich.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, this is how I was taken into the camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first night, they gave us the clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, we had the bunks, three tiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and for example, I was a young one so I could climb up on the highest one, on the tallest one, on the third bunk.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to leave our shoes in front of the bunks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course exhausted, hungry, and no food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the following probably was 4 o'clock in the morning, they come in yelling-- you can't even understand them-- raus, raus, get up.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
